{"tid":1503575,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[反制TickTack] 用歐盟《通用數據保障條例》拉停監控柱加裝，可行？","createTime":"2019-08-25T04:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T06:18:50.000Z","uid":219879,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9e741acb0c89f3913c6a9f4ad21d2d20e7caf9d7","tid":1503575,"uid":219879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"睇緊 ching 《TickTack 出左篇監控燈柱聲明》<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503220，我IT白癡但完全唔buy\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503220，我IT白癡但完全唔buy</a> Tick Tack DNS set 錯去上海監控柱同行到，fb 出地球po都無用！大家唔係IT唔代表無 bid 過政府 tender，邊啲人會贏心照啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入正題，我地有無辦法拉停三年內中環、金鐘、灣仔、銅鑼灣以及尖沙咀加裝監控柱？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n鬧上國際得唔得？<br />\n其中歐盟《通用數據保障條例》(GDPR) 係最嚴<br />\n<br />\n香港監控燈柱現時分佈觀塘同啟德，魔掌絕對會影到歐盟公民，如果資料直上大陸的話，Tick Tack 及香港監控柱有可能違反 GDPR ？有無違反&quot;特定的情況&quot;我唔識唔知，政府、Tick Tack 同上海三思唔該證明返點樣無！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>European Union (EU) - General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/data_privacy_law/eu/eu.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcpd.org.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fdata_privacy_law%2Feu%2Feu.html&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUG8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=f50fef9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcpd.org.hk/tc_chi/data_privacy_law/eu/eu.html</a><br />\n<br />\n《通用數據保障條例》對歐盟以外的資料保障局面帶來的其中一項重大發展，是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明確規定<span style=\"color: red;\">在非歐盟法域管轄區內成立的機構</span>在特定的情況下須遵從《通用數據保障條例》的規定。</span><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>略述歐盟《通用數據保障條例》及香港《個人資料（私隱）條例》的主要分別<br />\n<br />\n應用<br />\n<br />\n歐盟: 資料處理者或控制者：<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 在歐盟設立公司，或<br />\n<br />\n&bull; <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">在歐盟以外設立公司，提供貨品或服務，<span style=\"color: red;\">或監察歐盟人士的行為。</span></span> [第3條]<br />\n<br />\n香港: 資料使用者（控制者／處理者），獨自或聯同其他人或與其他人共同控制個人資料在香港或由香港收集、持有、處理或使用個人資料。 [第2(1)條]<br />\n<br />\n更多有關《通用數據保障條例》的資訊<br />\n<br />\n《香港律師》 (2018年6月份) - 歐盟《通用數據保障條例》與香港《個人資料（私隱）條例》有甚麼分別？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E3%80%8A%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8A%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%EF%BC%88%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%EF%BC%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E6%9C%89%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E5%88%86%E5%88%A5%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-lawyer.org%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E7%259B%259F%25E3%2580%258A%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%259C%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%258B%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E3%2580%258A%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25EF%25BC%2588%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1%25EF%25BC%2589%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%2588%25A5%25EF%25BC%259F&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUG8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=be675dee\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E3%80%8A%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8A%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%EF%BC%88%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%EF%BC%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E6%9C%89%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E5%88%86%E5%88%A5%EF%BC%9F</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n告 Tick Tack 違反 GDPR可行？<br />\n<br />\nfb地球 po 講到咁細嘅 start up 係咪就執？<br />\n<br />\n定又華麗轉身變另一隻白手套再出場？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉停監控柱！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac4cd54d2ba6bf3da1173d8ecc988a86d897cdf","tid":1503575,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"有無人有認識?? 幫幫手諗吖"},{"pid":"0582ba83e5ab978836ab9bed142968cab9d3b872","tid":1503575,"uid":219879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bac4cd54d2b